        <Parent_String>entablatures and entablature components [300052249], spanning and projecting structural elements [300078049], structural elements [300078048], structural elements and components for structural elements [300078046], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
